---
// Comparison component showing hilm.ai vs other tools
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-black">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        hilm.ai vs Other Tools
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        See how hilm.ai compares to spreadsheets, YNAB, Mint, ChatGPT, and other finance apps.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- ChatGPT Comparison Section -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">
        hilm.ai vs ChatGPT for Personal Finance
      </h2>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 mb-8">
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Many people wonder if they can use ChatGPT for money management. While ChatGPT is excellent for financial education and general advice, it cannot replace a specialized AI finance assistant like hilm.ai. Here's why:
        </p>

        <!-- Comparison Table -->
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700">
                <th class="text-left py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-white">Feature</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-white">hilm.ai</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-white">ChatGPT</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-gray-300">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Purpose</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">Specialized finance assistant</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">General-purpose AI</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Expense Tracking</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Automatic via text/voice/photos</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-400">❌ Manual entry only</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Transaction Categorization</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Automatic</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-400">❌ Not available</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Receipt Scanning</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ OCR-powered</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-400">❌ Not available</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Voice Input</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Optimized for expenses</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-400">⚠️ Limited</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Access to Your Financial Data</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Direct access</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-400">❌ Cannot access</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Personalized Insights</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Based on your data</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-400">❌ Generic only</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Real-Time Monitoring</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Available</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-400">❌ Not available</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Natural Language Finance Queries</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Optimized for finance</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Good</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-800">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Financial Education</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Good</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-400">✅ Excellent</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium">Monthly Cost</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">$16/month</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">$20/month (Plus)</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Key Takeaway</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            ChatGPT is excellent for learning about personal finance and getting general advice, but it cannot access your financial data or automatically track expenses. hilm.ai is purpose-built for expense tracking and provides personalized insights based on your actual spending patterns. Many users find value in using both: ChatGPT for education and hilm.ai for actual money management.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 text-center">
          <a
            href="/blog/chatgpt-for-money-management"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors"
          >
            Read more: ChatGPT for Money Management →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Other Comparisons -->
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">
        hilm.ai vs Traditional Finance Apps
      </h2>

      <!-- Comparison Cards -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <!-- vs Spreadsheets -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">vs Spreadsheets</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>No manual data entry—just send a message</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Automatic categorization with AI</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Natural language queries instead of formulas</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Works on any device via Telegram</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Receipt scanning and voice input</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- vs YNAB -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">vs YNAB</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Conversational interface—no forms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Lower cost: $16/month vs $14.99/month</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>AI-powered insights and recommendations</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Multiple input methods (text, voice, photos)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>No learning curve—just chat naturally</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- vs Mint -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">vs Mint</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Active development (Mint is shutting down)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Conversational AI interface</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Better privacy—no bank account linking required</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Personalized insights based on your data</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Voice and receipt photo support</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- vs Other Apps -->
        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">vs Other Finance Apps</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-300">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Purpose-built for conversational expense tracking</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>AI that learns your spending patterns</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>No complex setup or configuration</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Works seamlessly via Telegram</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-400 mt-1">✅</span>
              <span>Multi-currency support out of the box</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border-2 border-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-10 md:p-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Ready to Try hilm.ai?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Experience the future of expense tracking. Start with 5 free messages—no credit card required.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://t.me/hilmaibot"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-5 bg-white text-black font-bold text-lg rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transform hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-2xl shadow-white/40"
        >
          Start Your Free Trial
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

